<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>MorningSignal — {{ ticker }} Deep Dive</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:opsz,wght@9..144,600;9..144,700&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500;600&family=Manrope:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../assets/style.css">
  <link rel="icon" href="../assets/logo.svg" type="image/svg+xml">
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <div class="header-inner">
    <a href="../index.html" class="logo">
      <img src="../assets/logo.svg" width="32" height="32" alt="MorningSignal">
      <div>
        <div class="logo-text">Morning<span>Signal</span></div>
        <div class="logo-sub">Research Platform</div>
      </div>
    </a>
    <nav>
      <a href="../index.html">Home</a>
      <a href="../daily/{{ flagged_date }}.html">Daily Report</a>
      <a href="../dashboard.html">Dashboard</a>
      <a href="../industries.html">Industries</a>
      <a href="../investordebate.html">Debate</a>
      <a href="../archive.html">Archive</a>
    </nav>
    <div class="header-date">Deep Dive · {{ flagged_date }}</div>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="hero-strip">
  <div class="page-wrapper">
    <div class="deep-dive-header">
      <div class="flex-between">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">Persistent Breakout Candidate</div>
          <div class="deep-dive-ticker">
            {{ ticker }}
            {% if streak_days >= 3 %}
            <span class="flag-badge">★ {{ streak_days }} days</span>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
          <div class="deep-dive-name">{{ name }} · {{ sector }}</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="stat-value">${{ "%.2f"|format(price) }}</div>
          <div class="stat-meta {{ 'neg' if pct_from_high < 0 else 'pos' }}">{{ "%+.1f"|format(pct_from_high) }}% from 52W high (${{ "%.2f"|format(high_52w) }})</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="page-wrapper">

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div>
        <div class="section-kicker">Model Output</div>
        <div class="section-title">Composite Score Breakdown</div>
      </div>
      <div class="section-note">The score blends relative strength, base quality, trend structure, and stage confirmation.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="score-breakdown">
      <div class="score-component">
        <div class="score-component-label">Composite</div>
        <div class="score-component-value {{ 's-high' if score >= 80 else ('s-mid' if score >= 60 else 's-low') }}">{{ "%.1f"|format(score) }}</div>
        <div class="hero-mini-meta">
          <span class="badge {{ 'badge-green' if score >= 80 else ('badge-yellow' if score >= 60 else 'badge-gray') }}">
            {{ 'High Conviction' if score >= 80 else ('Developing' if score >= 60 else 'Watch') }}
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="score-component">
        <div class="score-component-label">Relative Strength</div>
        <div class="score-component-value {{ 's-high' if rs >= 80 else ('s-mid' if rs >= 60 else 's-low') }}">{{ "%.1f"|format(rs) }}</div>
        <div class="hero-mini-meta">IBD-style ranking vs. SPY</div>
      </div>
      <div class="score-component">
        <div class="score-component-label">Base Quality</div>
        <div class="score-component-value {{ 's-high' if base >= 80 else ('s-mid' if base >= 60 else 's-low') }}">{{ "%.1f"|format(base) }}</div>
        <div class="hero-mini-meta">SEPA-style structure check</div>
      </div>
      <div class="score-component">
        <div class="score-component-label">Trend Structure</div>
        <div class="score-component-value {{ 's-high' if trend >= 80 else ('s-mid' if trend >= 60 else 's-low') }}">{{ "%.1f"|format(trend) }}</div>
        <div class="hero-mini-meta">Moving-average alignment</div>
      </div>
      <div class="score-component">
        <div class="score-component-label">Stage 2</div>
        <div class="score-component-value {{ 'pos' if stage2 else 'neg' }}">{{ '✓' if stage2 else '✗' }}</div>
        <div class="hero-mini-meta">Weinstein stage filter</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">Technical Data</div>
    <div class="macro-grid">
      <div class="stat-card card">
        <div class="stat-label">Current Price</div>
        <div class="stat-value">${{ "%.2f"|format(price) }}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card card">
        <div class="stat-label">52-Week High</div>
        <div class="stat-value">${{ "%.2f"|format(high_52w) }}</div>
        <div class="stat-meta {{ 'neg' if pct_from_high < 0 else 'pos' }}">{{ "%+.1f"|format(pct_from_high) }}% from high</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card card">
        <div class="stat-label">Avg Daily Volume</div>
        <div class="stat-value">
          {% if avg_volume >= 1000000 %}
            {{ "%.1f"|format(avg_volume / 1000000) }}M
          {% else %}
            {{ "%.0f"|format(avg_volume / 1000) }}K
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card card">
        <div class="stat-label">Vol vs 50d Avg</div>
        <div class="stat-value {{ 'pos' if vol_ratio >= 1.4 else '' }}">{{ "%.2f"|format(vol_ratio) }}x</div>
        <div class="stat-meta">{{ 'Above-average volume confirmation' if vol_ratio >= 1.4 else 'Normal participation' }}</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">Appearance History</div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="mover-list">
        {% for entry in history %}
        <div class="mover-row">
          <div style="flex:1">
            <div class="archive-title">{{ entry.date }}</div>
            <div class="mover-caption">Rank #{{ entry.rank }}</div>
          </div>
          <span class="score-cell {{ 's-high' if entry.score >= 80 else ('s-mid' if entry.score >= 60 else 's-low') }}">{{ "%.1f"|format(entry.score) }}</span>
        </div>
        {% else %}
        <div class="note-card">This is the first recorded appearance for {{ ticker }} in the top-15 scan output.</div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">Interpretation</div>
    <div class="note-card">
      {{ ticker }} appeared in the top breakout list for <strong>{{ streak_days }} consecutive trading day{{ 's' if streak_days != 1 else '' }}</strong>, which is why it has a dedicated deep-dive page. Persistent appearances usually indicate a combination of strong relative strength, stable structure, and continued institutional-style sponsorship.
      <br><br>
      The next things to monitor are volume confirmation on breakouts, sector tailwinds, and any earnings-date proximity that could alter the setup quality quickly.
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<footer>
  <div>MorningSignal Research · Deep-dive generated for {{ flagged_date }} · Commentary is for research purposes only and not investment advice.</div>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
